style.css: @-moz-document url-prefix("http://www.tumblr.com"), url-prefix("https://www.tumblr.com") { .logo .logo-anchor:before { content: " " !important; } .logo .logo-anchor { height: 52px !important; width: 152px !important; margin: 0px 30px!important; display: block !important; background-size: auto 52px !important; background-image: url(https://static.tumblr.com/gwc9rra/oBZnecc43/logo-psych.png) !important; content: " " !important; } svg.svg-logo, .logo .png-logo, .logo .preload-container { display: none !important; } }
